Description:
You come across a young boy with a yellow rat surrounded by harmless monsters that fit the description the girl gave you, as you approach he says:

"Hi I'm Bash, I see you brought a monster egg so I assume my friend sent you to bring it to me, thank you very much.

As a reward I will train one of your pets and also give you some pets I tamed from the area.
DescriptionAction: Who do you want me to train?"
